係同具體措施去對香港同中國政府進行施壓，特別月尾前會通過所以情況緊急，可以的話請幫忙廣傳。<br />\n(之後提供當地簡單既官方請願方式)<br />\nーー<br />\n<br />\n各位如果知唔同地方既請願方式、主要流行既論壇都可以留言幫下手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1205217/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1205217/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"5e2562217b6ad73949d7830ae74ca8c320520923","tid":1204760,"uid":12609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T18:18:50.000Z","msg":"美國趕出黎既狗<br />\n支那見佢有少少利用價值<br />\n請佢做打手比啖狗飯佢食 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ca926416c16e1ea714a0198360d160c6a9f381d","tid":1204760,"uid":142067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T18:21:56.000Z","msg":"收哂錢啦，屌佢老母"},{"pid":"7648816784d01647ad886d3a35f67b852a488f84","tid":1204760,"uid":12609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d521c68e0c058343525fb6bf73e13213c648e024","tid":1204760,"uid":204929,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"65808417f962dadfc16cf4a8fbacbd13cf69ca0c","tid":1204760,"uid":12609,"like":143,"dislike":0,"score":143,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T16:09:16.000Z","msg":"奶共既仆街係有樣睇<br />\n樣樣衰衰好邪惡既撚樣"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T17:27:04.000Z","msg":"就算一定要睇講中國嗰啲鬼佬， 都唔會揀佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T18:28:20.000Z","msg":"睇開 Advchina同 China Uncensored<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c11040be055fccfd96573bd21e1a041ea56d0ec3","tid":1204760,"uid":22362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T18:28:23.000Z","msg":"入去直接屌佢老母就得"},{"pid":"f79b190c740673eacbeaaa63b384ede002c9539d","tid":1204760,"uid":204929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9aec89e60fb2109c0b7c3c21cce9033920db46ca","tid":1204760,"uid":258377,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T18:17:07.000Z","msg":"條鬼佬係咪新彊集中營放出嚟架<img src=\"/asset